{
  "stem": "4361.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She began to count each time with her numbered what she was supposed to have.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she kept counting and counting and made mistakes, and somebody wasn't there, and then this went on and on and on for hours sometimes.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then came the [GERMAN] to count.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Again, she too didn't have the exact numbers, or somebody just fell down, passed out-- again, counting.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the final count was done by the SS.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The SS counted, but at the same time, weeded, selected.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so the numbers we didn't still know why, although by this time, two weeks later, the old timers, as we used to call them, whom we constantly kept asking, tell us.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When are we going to meet our mothers, our children, et cetera?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They would say, see?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's where they went.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "At first, I remember clearly saying to myself, this poor woman lost her mind.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean she's crazy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I mean everybody knows it's a bakery.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It has a funny smell, but it's a bakery.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, somehow two, three weeks later, we know it was not a bakery.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And even though we didn't talk about it, even I didn't talk about it to anyone, I knew the second big lie [BACKGROUND NOISE] when the SS so politely said to me, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But Miss, we are civilized people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You are going to see your mother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was a Hungarian-- you see, after four or six weeks of quarantine--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I believe in Lager A, which is part of Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, Birkenau is part of Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had Lager A, B, C.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "B was the work Lager.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "C was the worst, and at the time I got to C, I called this Anus Mundi, which you know probably what it means.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
